ouve-probably-never-heard-of-180988789/</link><description>根据国家历史保护信托基金的最新名单，从革命战争战场到民权时代的避风港，这些历史遗迹正面临风险</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 20:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/to-mark-americas-250th-birthday-see-the-countrys-most-endangered-places-that-youve-probably-never-heard-of-180988789/</guid></item><item><title>观看美国宇航局在小行星战略飞越过程中拍摄到的令人惊叹的火星新图像</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-nasas-stunning-new-images-of-mars-captured-during-an-asteroid-bound-spacecrafts-strategic-flyby-180988788/</link><description>5 月 15 日，Psyche 任务在研究一颗同名小行星的途中接近了这颗红色星球 2,864 英里的范围内</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 20:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-nasas-stunning-new-images-of-mars-captured-during-an-asteroid-bound-spacecrafts-strategic-flyby-180988788/</guid></item><item><title>杰克逊·波洛克希望通过这幅令人眼花缭乱的水滴画来实现什么，这幅画刚刚以破纪录的 1.81 亿美元成交？</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/what-did-jackson-pollock-hope-to-accomplish-with-this-dizzying-drip-painting-which-just-sold-for-a-record-breaking-181-million-180988794/</link><description>这位抽象表现主义者以其动作绘画而闻名，强调艺术家在创作过程中身体的运动。 《Number 7A, 1948》现在是他拍卖过的最昂贵的作品</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 19:51:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/what-did-jackson-pollock-hope-to-accomplish-with-this-dizzying-drip-painting-which-just-sold-for-a-record-breaking-181-million-180988794/</guid></item><item><title>新研究发现，古埃及的工程选择帮助吉萨大金字塔在地震中幸存下来</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ancient-egyptian-engineering-choices-helped-the-great-pyramid-of-giza-survive-earthquakes-new-research-finds-180988790/</link><description>研究人员测量了金字塔内部和周围的振动，发现该结构具有惊人的抗震能力</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 18:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/ancient-egyptian-engineering-choices-helped-the-great-pyramid-of-giza-sur